Slow Cooker Spicy Spinach Artichoke Dip
  --Haley Aldoroty

10 oz bag baby spinach
14 oz can of artichokes, drained and chopped
1 block cream cheese, cubed
3/4 c sour cream
1/4 c mayo
3 cloves garlic, grated
1 large shallots, minced
1 c grated mozzarella cheese
1 c grated parmesan cheese
2 tsp chopped calabrian chilis (more if you have a higher spice tolerance)
1 tsp kosher salt
1/2 tsp black pepper
tortilla chips to serve

Put all ingredients in the slow cooker. Gently mix together. Cover and cook on low for 2 hr, stirring halfway through. Serve with tortilla chips.


